            <tr>
              <td colspan="3" class="ourfocus"><strong>Our focus</strong> is the production 
            of metal fabrications, steel ducts, tanks, assemblies, heavy equipment 
            components, stampings and steel structures. In short we stamp, form, 
            weld, fabricate, assemble, roll, bend, cut, CNC machine, turn, face 
            and finish metal. We work with mild steel, stainless steel and aluminum. 
            We combine our welding and fabricating skills with press capability 
            to 1500 tons. Thus, we are unique in blanking, stamping and forming 
            heavy gauge metal. We offer open press time, flexible lead times and 
            custom tool design. We build our own tooling. Tooling design and build 
            is an important service to our customers. We maintain a presence in 
            a variety of markets including but not limited to; Off-highway construction 
            and agricultural equipment, automotive, heavy machinery, bulk handling 
            equipment, plant process equipment, refinery equipment and a broad 
            range of material handling industries. We maintain a solid business 
            in proprietary heavy duty material handling products marketed and 
            sold directly to the end user or through dealers and distributors. 
            Specifically we manufacture structural steel racks and customized 
            material handling and storage products. Our racks service a variety 
            of markets including but not limited to; metal service centers, lumber 
            yards and retailers in carpets, vinyl, flooring and home improvement 
            products.</td> 
            </tr>
